'''Edilson Alberto Monteiro Sanches Borges''' ({{IPA|pt|e.ˈdil.sɔn al.ˈbɛɾ.tu mõ.ˈtej.ɾu ˈsɐ̃.ʃɨʒ ˈbɔɾ.ʒɨʃ|lang}}; born 17 January 1995), known as '''Diney''' ({{IPA|kea|di.ˈnej|lang}}), is a Cape Verdean professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[UAE Pro League]] club [[Al Bataeh Club|Al Bataeh]] and the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].

==Club career==
Diney started his youth career with [[Vitória F.C.]] in 2010,<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oceanpress.info/cms/Pt/desporto/3781-madeira-diney-assina-por-cinco-anos-com-o-maritimo |title=Ocean Press - Madeira - Diney assina por cinco anos com o Marítimo |access-date=11 December 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806183930/http://www.oceanpress.info/cms/Pt/desporto/3781-madeira-diney-assina-por-cinco-anos-com-o-maritimo |archive-date=6 August 2017 |url-status=dead }}</ref> before joining [[C.S. Marítimo B|Marítimo B]]. On 30 November 2014, Diney made his professional debut with Marítimo B in a [[2014–15 Segunda Liga]] match against [[C.D. Santa Clara|Santa Clara]].{{citation needed|date=September 2025}} After good performances, Diney was promoted to Marítimo's first team squad, making his league debut against [[C.F. União]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/uniao-madeira/maritimo/jogo/13503389|title=Jogo União Madeira - Marítimo - Liga NOS - Maisfutebol.iol.pt|website=Maisfutebol}}</ref>

On 13 June 2018, he joined [[G.D. Estoril Praia|Estoril]].<ref>{{cite news | date=13 June 2018 | title=Diney regressa ao Continente para brilhar no Estoril Praia| url=http://estorilpraia.pt/diney-regressa-ao-continente-para-brilhar-no-estoril-praia/| publisher=estorilpraia.pt| access-date=16 June 2018 }}</ref>

On 4 July 2023, Emirati club [[Al Bataeh Club]] announced the signing of Diney.<ref>{{cite news | date=4 July 2023 | title=رسميا/ البطائح الإماراتي يعلن تعاقده مع بورغيس قادما من الجيش الملكي | url=https://www.elbotola.com/article/2023-07-04-17-35-856.html | publisher=elbotola.com | access-date=4 July 2023 }}</ref>

==International career==
Diney made his debut for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]] in a 4–0 [[2018 FIFA World Cup qualification]] loss to [[Burkina Faso national football team|Burkina Faso]] on 14 November 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/matches/round=276412/match=300367127/index.html#lineups|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819093835/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/matches/round=276412/match=300367127/index.html#lineups|url-status=dead|archive-date=19 August 2016|title=2018 FIFA World Cup Russia - Matches - Burkina Faso-Cape Verde Islands |website=FIFA.com}}</ref>

